---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Free Resources | Social Magic with Jen"
  description="Free tools and guides to help women-owned service businesses build marketing that sounds like them. Start with The Marketing Alignment Audit."
  keywords="free marketing resources, marketing audit for small business, women-owned business marketing tools, brand voice resources"
  canonical="https://socialmagicwithjen.com/resources"
  ogDescription="Free tools to help you spot the gap between marketing that's 'good enough' and marketing that actually builds trust."
  ogImage="https://socialmagicwithjen.com/images/jen-portrait.jpg"
  ogImageWidth="1279"
  ogImageHeight="1600"
>
<style>
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--plum); }
.nav-links a { position: relative; padding: 4px 0; }
.nav-links a::after { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; bottom: -2px; width: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--coral); transition: width 0.25s ease; }
.nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }

nav {
  position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
  background: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.92);
  backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(78, 58, 90, 0.08);
}
nav .wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 84px; gap: 16px; }
.logo { font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--plum); display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.logo .magic-word { color: var(--coral); }
.logo .with-jen { font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--gold); }
.nav-cta {
  background: var(--coral); color: var(--cream); padding: 11px 24px; border-radius: 999px;
  font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease; white-space: nowrap;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--coral-deep); transform: translateY(-1px); }

@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .nav-links { display: none; }
}

/* Page content */
.hero {
  padding: 72px 24px 56px;
  text-align: center;
}
.eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
  font-size: 22px;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin: 0 0 8px 0;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
  margin: 0 0 18px 0;
}
.hero p {
  max-width: 620px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--ink);
}

.resource-grid {
  max-width: var(--max);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 32px 96px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 28px;
}

.resource-card {
  background: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 36px 32px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(78, 58, 90, 0.08);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 14px;
}

.resource-tag {
  align-self: flex-start;
  background: rgba(95, 168, 168, 0.14);
  color: var(--teal);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 5px 12px;
  border-radius: 999px;
}

.resource-card h2 {
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  margin: 0;
}

.resource-card p {
  font-size: 0.98rem;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.65;
}

.resource-btn {
  margin-top: auto;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-self: flex-start;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px 26px;
  background: var(--coral);
  color: var(--cream);
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  transition: transform 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease;
}
.resource-btn:hover { background: var(--coral-deep); transform: translateY(-2px); }

/* Placeholder card for what's coming */
.resource-card.coming-soon {
  background: transparent;
  border: 1.5px dashed rgba(78, 58, 90, 0.2);
  box-shadow: none;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--plum-soft);
}
.resource-card.coming-soon h2 { color: var(--plum-soft); font-size: 1.15rem; }

.footer-note {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 0 24px 80px;
}
.footer-note p {
  font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  color: var(--gold);
}
</style>

<nav id="site-nav">
  <div class="wrap">
    <a href="/" class="logo">Social<span class="magic-word">Magic</span><span class="with-jen">with jen</span></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/#method">The Method</a>
      <a href="/#fit">Is This You?</a>
      <a href="/#about">About Jen</a>
      <a href="/#faq">FAQ</a>
      <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
      <a href="/resources">Resources</a>
    </div>
    <a href="/#contact" class="nav-cta">Let's Get Started</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">free resources &#10022;</p>
  <h1>Marketing clarity, no strings attached</h1>
  <p>Real tools to help you spot the gap between marketing that's "good enough" and marketing that actually sounds like you. Start here, no pressure, just clarity.</p>
</section>

<div class="resource-grid">

  <div class="resource-card">
    <span class="resource-tag">Self-Audit</span>
    <h2>The Marketing Alignment Audit</h2>
    <p>Nine assets. One system. A self-audit that helps you spot where your website, emails, social, and AI stop sounding like each other, and start sounding like one clear brand.</p>
    <a href="https://social-magic-with-jen.kit.com/f55b300db3" class="resource-btn">Get the Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <div class="resource-card">
    <span class="resource-tag">Worksheet</span>
    <h2>The Brand Voice Starter Kit</h2>
    <p>Five quick exercises to find the words that actually sound like you. A worksheet to help your website, emails, and social posts finally sound like the same person wrote them.</p>
    <a href="https://social-magic-with-jen.kit.com/b01ed86db6" class="resource-btn">Get the Kit &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <div class="resource-card coming-soon">
    <h2>More on the way &#10022;</h2>
    <p>New tools and guides are in the works. Join The Spark so you're the first to know when they land.</p>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="footer-note">
  <p>more magic coming soon</p>
</div>

</Layout>
